4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence. This comprehensive 6-week program is designed for professionals who want to leverage the power of AI in their current roles. The course covers various topics, including the different types of generative AI, key elements like context, prompts, and models, and best practices for AI integration. The classes are held online, with two live sessions per week. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people. Upon completion of the course, participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. No previous experience is required to enroll in the course. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course. stop